[[Translation:Main/en/Cycle signal types]]
{{en/-}}
Set which type of signal should be cycled through when ctrl-clicking on a ready-built signal. Choose between cycling through all [[Main/en/signal]] types, just the [[Main/en/block signals]] types or only the [[Main/en/path signals]] types.

0 = Block signals only
1 = Path signals only
2 = All

See also: [[Main/en/Advanced Settings/Construction#Cycle through signal types]]